data.text:
2014 was a great year for girls to participate in so many beauty competitions. As you know there’s always a winner in every competition. The following list is made of 5 first girls who should have or who represented Africa in different beauty competitions.

Sheillah Shadia, born in August 1995, is a Rwandan by nationality, who is taken by the passion love for fashion.
